{"tid":1121532,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱喺LingU屌到個00後學生跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-04-23T11:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T12:42:02.000Z","uid":150100,"like":1139,"dislike":545,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab8c5758d337a95863578cfa7fda5ec5a730a32","tid":1121532,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早排見廣告話咩LingU係亞洲十大頂尖博雅教育學府又盛<br />\n咁今日見去開屯門<br />\n咪順路去參觀下囉<br />\n<br />\n咁一入校門，就見到個一睇就係00後嘅懵炳喺Lecture room門口排隊<br />\n我見佢個樣低低地咪過去撩下佢<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n00後：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：依間大學嚟㗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩勁喎大學生嚟喎，你Dse幾分入嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：18<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：18分入到嘅都叫大學？咁Asso仔都係大學生啦，Ive都叫大學啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁...咁我真係大學生喎<br />\n<br />\n我聽到即刻火都嚟埋<br />\n一嘢喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢俾我嘅氣勢嚇到一嘢跪咗喺度喊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n我嗰個年代18分返鄉下執牛屎咋<br />\n18分都自稱大學生，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬咁<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我先停，放佢一馬<br />\n反正啲低等人種都屌唔醒㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好型"},{"pid":"75011d2345aef16acf868f8eae69fe0f4db031d5","tid":1121532,"uid":12707,"like":1099,"dislike":14,"score":1085,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"你唔撚厭既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d5e0c5b8059e519800b18de1e535ee5ed12bb","tid":1121532,"uid":150100,"like":17,"dislike":214,"score":-197,"quote":{"pid":"75011d2345aef16acf868f8eae69fe0f4db031d5","tid":1121532,"uid":12707,"like":1099,"dislike":14,"score":1085,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"你唔撚厭既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"6dedce38f32b7fe55b2e92159db4473df2fc5435","tid":1121532,"uid":71508,"like":18,"dislike":35,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"00後唔屌唔duck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf0a0eb9d34fa5eeba3469bd619b4a73e4558d5","tid":1121532,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6dedce38f32b7fe55b2e92159db4473df2fc5435","tid":1121532,"uid":71508,"like":18,"dislike":35,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"00後唔屌唔duck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"4359d2a4c7fea873739ac360eb2078523fb7760b","tid":1121532,"uid":123456,"like":154,"dislike":6,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下次佢地跪喺到<br />\n逼佢地幫你含到射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"fa6f57c83994cd4e587214ee2d0dcf000eb12cdf","tid":1121532,"uid":150100,"like":9,"dislike":59,"score":-50,"quote":{"pid":"4359d2a4c7fea873739ac360eb