火都嚟埋<br />\n一嘢喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢俾我嘅氣勢嚇到一嘢跪咗喺度喊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n我嗰個年代18分返鄉下執牛屎咋<br />\n18分都自稱大學生，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬咁<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我先停，放佢一馬<br />\n反正啲低等人種都屌唔醒㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你 垃圾就咪撚係度開po啦 作故仔作撚到你"},{"pid":"cc4f6446e323b3a8c5b1685a4a98a48e60a077c6","tid":1121532,"uid":206655,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1n7Aw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1n7Aw9.png&h=69b2be00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dae40398bba652b59c226f04c617a27bb0f03ba8","tid":1121532,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7d5e0c5b8059e519800b18de1e535ee5ed12bb","tid":1121532,"uid":150100,"like":17,"dislike":214,"score":-197,"quote":{"pid":"75011d2345aef16acf868f8eae69fe0f4db031d5","tid":1121532,"uid":12707,"like":1099,"dislike":14,"score":1085,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"你唔撚厭既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face